Daily-driver bundle (rc parity)

- [x] External command lookup honors $path for all execs
- [x] Add builtin: which (inspect $path)
- [x] Subshell executes in a forked process (rc-style isolation)
- [x] Add builtin: wait (for background jobs)
- [x] Add builtin: shift
- [x] Add builtin: return (function exit)
- [x] Add builtin: eval (parse and run string)
- [x] Add builtin: newpgrp (rc compatibility)
- [ ] Full fd redirection syntax: >[fd], <[fd], dup forms
- [x] Named pipe forms <{ ... } and >{ ... } execution (nmpipe)
